| **Sweet spot** | **G-VS2** | **[$36,883](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29441823?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)** | **29441823** |
| Sweet spot | G-VS2 | [$38,241](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28557634?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 28557634 |
| Mid | F-VS2 | [$44,156](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/27893612?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 27893612 |
| Premium | E-VS2 | [$48,730](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29034817?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 29034817 |
| Premium | D-VS2 | [$53,419](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28674539?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 28674539 |
| VVS | G-VVS2 | [$47,285](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29523841?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 29523841 |
| VVS | E-VVS1 | [$58,943](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28391627?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 28391627 |
